name: Compliance Xpressware
tag_list: compliance, edgar, sec, software, xbrl, sec-html, cloud, regulatory-compliance, edgar-filing
overview:
CX is a Silicon Valley based SEC EDGAR compliance software solutions company.

With deep roots in innovations and cutting-edge software development, CX prides itself in building software solutions based on 100% proprietary technologies. The current focus is on public company compliance with US SEC reporting. Future solutions will address other compliance needs in the US and other parts of the World.
